s suddenly winning!} Qa5+ (11... Ndf6 12. Bxe6+ Ke8 13. Qg6#) 12. Bd2 Qf5 13. Qxf5+ {Many people try to defend like that, just forgetting that the pawn is pinned on e6 .} *

