f6 23. g5 $1 hxg5 24. hxg5 Bh5 25. gxf6 $3 Bxf3 26. f7+ Kh7 27. Rh5# {. What a beautiful, angelic checkmate. Feel free to see the game reaction on YouTube – Brilliant Queen Sacrifice with Alien Gambit .}) 15. c4 {Kicking the active pony on d5 .} Nf6 16. h4 g4 17. Qe3 Bg7 18. Bc2 h5 19. g3 {Black is a piece up, but White has a positional bind, and in bullet or blitz, it is super duper difficult to play for Black, as they cannot develop their kingside and their king is always weak.} *

