k king is weak.} Bxe5 11. dxe5 Nd5 12. Qg4 {Nf8 c4} Nb6 {Bc2 Bd7} 13. Be3 Qe7 14. Rad1 Qf7 $2 15. Bc5 $1 {Be8 Re3! Nbd7 Rf3!} Qh5 {Rxd7!! Mindblowing queen sacrifice. The pony on f8 is now hanging. Qxg4} (15... Bd7 {, now the queen on h5 is hanging.} 16. Qh5 {, and if Nxd7 Qxe6+ Bf7 Qxd7+- .White is winning, as all their pieces are active, e6 is coming, and Black is getting mated.})) *

