his is the move I recommend! Preparing the very strong Qe3 - g3 queen transfer to the kingside.} b6 14. Qe3 Bb7 15. Qg3 { It is a very good idea to transfer the queen to the kingside. The pin from the bishop on d6 is not dangerous, as f4 will come at the right moment, but now we threaten Bxh6 . I think I have won all my games in this position. It's just so easy to play for White here.} *

