e rookie will be defended after} 16. Nxf8 Nxf8 17. Qxf8+ Kd7 $1 18. Qf7 g5 $1 {The queen is trapped.}) ({After} 15... Rc8 $1 16. h3 Qf5 17. Nxf8 $4 Nxf8 18. Qxf8+ Kd7 19. Qf7 g5 {, White's queen is trapped so the best move here is to resign.}) 16. Bf4+ Kb6 17. Rfe1 {Developing with tempi always feels good.} Qxc2 18. Qxe6 a6 19. Rac1 Qa4 20. Be3 Ka7 21. d5+ c5 22. Rxc5 ({ Brilliant! Sacrificing the rookie to clear the g1 - a7 diagonal. Now Black's defense is destroyed: Nxc5} 22. Bxc5+ b6 23. Qxb6+ {.}) *

