13. Rb1 Qxc3 14. Rxb7 Nd5 15. Qa4 {SO ROMANTIC!! OMG OMG, this is too beautiful! Sacrificing the bishop.} Nb4 (15... Nxf4 16. Rxb8+ $3 {Brilliant!! Removing the defender of the c6 -pawn:} Rxb8 17. Qxc6+ Kd8 18. Qd7# {.}) 16. Qxa7 {Sacrifice THE QUEEN!!! for daddy issues, aka back rank issues.} Rxa7 17. Rxb8# {CM Witty_Alien (2393) vs. MarioBayatov (1819), Jul 12, 2024.} *

