. Bd2 Qb6 15. Ng6 {and the position is chaos, but Black is much better, as they are a piece up.}) 13. Ng6 {Tada! The rookie is trapped, as Black cannot take due to checkmate.} Qa5+ (13... Bxg6 $4 14. Bxg6#) 14. Bd2 Qb6 15. Nxh8 {White is better, as they are material up.} *

