ing a vital pawn.} Bd5 12. Qd3 {Sacrificing the rookie and the bishop on e6 for the mate on g6 . So romantic.} Qa5+ (12... Bxe6 13. Qg6+ Bf7 14. Qxf7#) 13. Bd2 Qc7 14. Qg6+ Kd8 15. Nf7+ Ke8 16. Nd6+ Kd8 17. Qe8+ {Brilliant!! Sacrificing The queen to do some-kinda of central smother-mate. What a beauty!} Nxe8 18. Nf7# {I have won so many games like that. And those wonderful people who watch my videos and streams, probably have seen this.} *

