k is by attacking the center.} 9... Nbd7 $4 10. Nxe6 $3) 10. dxc5 Bxc5 11. Bf4 {Brilliant!! One way to farm brilliant moves in chess.com. :) )))))) White is preparing to castle big.} hxg5 {Taking a few moves later meets the same faith on the h-file.} 12. hxg5 Nd5 13. Bh7+ Kh8 14. Qe4 f5 15. Bxf5+ { That is check! White is completely winning.} Kg8 16. Bxe6+ Bxe6 17. Qxe6+ Rf7 18. g6 {The rookie on f7 is gone and so is the game for Black.} *

