hen they will lose. The opening of the h-file 100% favors White, who has more active pieces.} 9... Nbd7 $4 10. Nxe6 $3) 10. hxg5 Nd5 11. Bh7+ Kh8 12. Ne5 Bxe5 13. Bg6+ Kg8 14. Rh8+ ({Damiano's Mate!! It's important that the queen comes to the h-file with check. Otherwise, ... fxg6 would win for Black. We can see how strong the h-file is and the pony sacrifice on g5 is fully justified: Kxh8} 14. Qh5 {Kg8 Qh7# .}) *

